package com.flipkart.business
  • Class
    Description
    FlipFitAdminInterface
    Interface defining the operations that an admin can perform in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitAdminService
    Provides business logic for administrative tasks including approving or rejecting gym owners and gyms, and managing gym and owner data.
    FlipFitCustomerInterface
    Interface defining the operations that can be performed by a customer in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitCustomerService
    Service class implementing the FlipFitCustomerInterface.
    FlipFitGymOwnerInterface
    Interface defining the operations that can be performed by a gym owner in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitGymOwnerService
    Provides business logic for gym owner operations including managing gym profiles, gyms, slots, and bookings.
    FlipFitPaymentsInterface
    Interface for managing payments in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitPaymentsService
    Service class for handling payment operations in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitSlotBookingInterface
    Interface for managing slot bookings in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitSlotBookingService
    Service class for managing slot bookings in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitUserInterface
    Interface for user-related operations in the FlipFit system.
    FlipFitUserService
    Service class for user-related operations in the FlipFit system.
